ucm (1.8.0-beta) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New features:
    - Enhanced Docker infrastructure with comprehensive ENV configuration
    - Add Gunicorn deployment with native mTLS support
    - Implement hybrid mTLS authentication (native + reverse proxy)
    - Add global loading indicator for page navigation and login

  * Bug fixes:
    - Make loading indicator background transparent to avoid flash
    - Add padding: 0 to table cards for rounded corners

  * Other changes:
    - fix(settings): Remove leftover JavaScript code causing syntax error
    - refactor(settings): Replace inline mTLS config with link to dedicated page
    - feat(mtls): Add dynamic reverse proxy configuration guide
    - perf: Add Flask-Caching for dashboard and SMTP config
    - security: Fix XSS vulnerabilities and add input validation
    - docs: Add comprehensive code audit report
    - feat(notifications): Add My Notification Settings section with user email preference
    - refactor(notifications): Hide SMTP config for non-admin users, simplify UI labels
    - refactor(ui): Remove mTLS Authentication from sidebar (moved to Settings page)
    - feat(ui): Add My Certificates to sidebar under My Account section


 -- UCM Development Team <dev@ucm-project.org>  Fri, 09 Jan 2026 19:36:33 +0100
